Package edu.northwestern.at.utils.corpuslinguistics.thesaurus Description

Thesaurus.

A Thesaurus provides synonyms (word related in meaning) and antonyms (words opposite in meaning) to a specified word.

All MorphAdorner thesauruses must implement the Thesaurus interface. The ThesaurusFactory provides the mechanism for instantiating a default or specified instance of a thesaurus implementation.
